Individuals — New Vernon Wealth Management













































New Vernon Wealth Management














Individuals & Families



Our Family Office is Your Family Office. Due to our origins as a family office we are especially attuned to the needs of families and professionals.Whether it's planning for retirement, managing inheritance, funding childrens' education or other financial matters, we have the experience of helping clients through life's inevitable transitions.We understand that each family has unique objectives and circumstances.  Each relationship receives the thoughtfulness and personal attention required to develop and implement the most appropriate investment strategies in an effort to achieve those objectives.Our team works closely with all your investment advisors including lawyers, estate planners, financial planners and insurers. 



















