New Vernon Investment Management LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 11:46 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of New Vernon Investment Management LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
New Vernon Investment Management LLC is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to the pooled investment vehicles. It invests in equity and fixed income markets across the globe. New Vernon Investment Management LLC is based in Highland Park, Illinois with an additional office in Jersey City, New Jersey.


